The paper proposes a new neural network building block for IoT applications that integrates the Short-Time Fourier Transform, a widely-used time-frequency analysis method, into data processing to learn features directly in the frequency domain. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), systems and control (cs.SY), and information theory (cs.IT).
